To get perplexity of any sentence, run the following command:
- python3 language_model.py <n_value> <smoothing type> <path to corpus>

A prompt will appear asking for an input. Give the input sentence and it will return the perplexity of that sentence for given value of n, smoothing type and corpus input.


To get perplexity of each sentence on the europarl or medical corpus, comment out the following parts:
1) Where we are taking parameter argument
2) Where if conditions based on the parameters is written
3) Remove the smoothing type argument from perplexity function

and uncomment the last part of the code and run it using the following command:
- python3 language_model.py
